description: 보랏빛 노을이 지는 몽환적인 놀이공원, 스타(STAR)가 회전목마 앞에 서서 비눗방울을 불고 있습니다. 비눗방울 안에는 도시 사람들의 잊혀진 꿈들이 홀로그램처럼 비치고, 그녀는 신비로운 표정으로 그것을 바라봅니다.
visual_concept: Dreamy amusement park at magic hour with a purple and pink sunset sky. A doll-like girl in a lavender sweater stands before a glowing carousel. She blows soap bubbles that reflect miniature, holographic dreamscapes inside them. The scene is surreal and soft, with a hazy, nostalgic filter applied to the background lights.
camera_movement: slow orbit around the character, focusing on the reflection in the bubbles
lighting: Soft purple and pink ambient light from the sunset, mixed with the warm yellow glow of the carousel lights
